@title README Controller app

DESCRIPTION
--------------------------------------------------
This application shall be the sensor mote. The node sends the packets
to the coordinator every DEFAULT_RATE ms. If a packet has successfully sent the GREEN LED
blinks..

The sensor node has to have an ID = 2 * WT_NUMBER - 1, otherwise he
will not receive the packets of his process.

In the PCB board the sensor node corresponds to the upper one.

Different options has been shown in the general README file
(CentralizedControllerGeneral/README)